name: Don't Collide (ato Games)
description: Don't collide is a 2d game where you have to move the player from the start base to the end line without hitting or touching any obstacles around you. Movements in Don't Collide depends on using triggers against the gravity where letting the trigger could cost you a life. This 1st version contains 10 levels and more levels will be added near. Feel free to leave feedback so you can help us to improve.
